
Overview of noun mistress

The noun mistress has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                       
1. (4) mistress, kept woman, fancy woman -- (an adulterous woman; a woman who has an ongoing extramarital sexual relationship with a man)
2. schoolmarm, schoolma'am, schoolmistress, mistress -- (a woman schoolteacher (especially one regarded as strict))
3. mistress -- (a woman master who directs the work of others)
